  "prompt": "What is the best HD led TV under 20000 rupees?",
  "response": "As of the latest information available, there are several options for HD LED TVs under 20,000 rupees that offer good features and performance. Here are a few of the top choices:\n\n1. **Mi TV 4A PRO** - This TV comes with a 32-inch HD Ready display, Android TV, and features like PatchWall, Google Assistant, and built-in Chromecast.\n\n2. **Samsung Wondertainment Series HD Ready LED TV** - Samsung is known for its display quality. The 32-inch Wondertainment Series offers a great viewing experience with PurColor and HDR support.\n\n3. **LG HD Ready Smart LED TV** - LG\u2019s 32-inch HD Ready Smart TV offers HDR support, Active HDR, and webOS for smart features. It also has the ThinQ AI support.\n\n4. **Sony Bravia HD Ready LED TV** - Sony's 32-inch Bravia series offers high-quality picture and sound. It includes X-Reality PRO technology and smart features.\n\n5. **TCL HD Ready Smart LED TV** - TCL offers a 32-inch HD Ready TV with features like smart TV capabilities, built-in Chromecast, and voice controls.\n\nAlways check the latest prices and reviews before making a purchase, as prices and models can frequently update. Ensure that the TV meets your requirements in terms of features and quality.",
